data.content_en: All the bright, precious things fade so fast, and they don’t come back.
data.content_zh: 所有的光鲜亮丽都敌不过时间，并且一去不复返。

data.content_en: It was an age of miracles, it was an age of art, it was an age of excess, and it was an age of satire.
data.content_zh: 这是一个奇迹的时代，一个艺术的时代，一个挥金如土的时代，也是一个充满嘲讽的时代。
